	"blackD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Acid",
    	"blueD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Lightning",
    	"brassD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Fire",
    	"bronzeD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Lightning",
    	"copperD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Acid",
    	"goldD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Fire",
    	"greenD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Poison",
    	"redD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Fire",
    	"silverD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Cold",
    	"whiteD": "Your bloodline descends from a draconic ancestor. You have resistance to the following damage type. Your Breath Weapon also deals this type of damage.<br><b>Damage type:</b> Cold",
        "cloudsJauntD": "As a bonus action, you can magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see.",
        "firesBurnD": "When you hit a target with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can deal an extra 1d10 fire damage to that target.",
        "frostsChillD": "When you hit a target with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can deal an extra 1d6 cold damage to that target and reduce its speed by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.",
        "hillsTumbleD": "When you hit a large or smaller creature with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can knock that creature prone.",
        "stonesEnduranceD": "When you take damage, you can use a reaction to roll 1d12. Add your Constitution modifier to that roll and reduce the damage by that total.",
        "stormsThunderD": "When you take damage from a creature within 60 feet, you can use a reaction to deal 1d8 thunder damage to that creature.",

